com.mattkinloch.softwareengineering

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mattkinloch.softwareengineering.Location

  • public class Location
extends java.lang.Object
    The location of a user in the system. The location is used to get a geo object to identify a range of listings in their area when searching for available appointments to book.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Matt Kinloch, Scott Guetens
